This amazing collaborative animation between @c_bass3d and @neoporkog beautifully captures with amazing sights we will see when Starship leaves Earth for the first time!

You can watch the full YouTube video here:
https://youtu.be/iFt_LsFRFEQ
⚠️it's 8 minutes of pure awesomeness⚠️
.
.
Follow @neoporkog and @c_bass3d on here aswell as twitter for more amazing work!
.
.

.

To celebrate us reaching an amazing milestone of 400K followers! We are releasing our new HLS program poster, shirt and hoodies! SpaceX has been through a turbulent situation with NASA. You can now show your support towards your favourite HLS lander design. 

To say thank you, use HLS400K for 30% off all our designs. Link in the bio!

Credit to @tomdixondesign and @austin8barnard  for designing us these amazing posters!
.

Two yrs ago yesterday, StarHopper flew to its 150m apogee and successfully landed. And moments after, SpaceX allowed us to run up to the pad and document their first small success of the StarShip program. It is still one of my most treasured memories to this day!✨

📷 Credit to @tmahlmann for the great photography!
